description	"Archetype: Sith Juggernaut

Class: Sith.
Class Summary: 
A massive tanky Sith with high-powered, hard-hitting and long-reaching lightsaber attacks who cannot be knocked back by blaster fire.

Lightsaber
- Defense (2)
- Deflect (2)
- Can use Red and Purple styles
- Has significantly increased Block and Attack Power

Force Powers:
- Jump (3)
- Push (2)
- Pull (3)
- Lightning (3)
- Sense	(2)
- Force Block (1)
- Force Focus (1)

Attributes:
- Strength (2) (Immune to Push/Pull, no knockback from blasters)
- Heal (1)

~Desann: A Chistori Force-sensitive who was outcasted by his native people, Desann was one of Luke's first students at the Jedi Academy on Yavin IV. 
However, he slowly became more and more cruel and turned to the Dark Side. 
----------
~Darth Malgus: Known and feared throughout the galaxy for his power with the dark side, military prowess, and sheer cruelty, Darth Malgus nearly brought about the destruction of both the Galactic Republic and Jedi Order."